      "text": "Spider-Man  is a side-scrolling action game developed by Western Technologies and published by Acclaim and LJN in 1995, based on the 1994–98 animated series of the same name. The game was released for the Sega Genesis and the Super Nintendo Entertainment System (SNES). The two versions of the game have the same basic story but have gameplay, level, and enemy differences.",
